<item>
            <title>[LU-13930] Auto PCC-RO attach in atomic_open</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13930</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Auto PCC-RO attach during PCC open will try to change the layout to read-only state on MDT. If&#160;the intent open in atomic_open returns the lock with&#160;MDS_INODELOCK_LAYOUT bit set, it may cause dead&#160;lock. Thus it would better to release the&#160;intent lock first before call PCC open.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
